Chhai2-giok8 chi2-moai7 lai5 tau3-kha-chhiu2 liau2-au7, kai2-sian7 liau2 in ka-teng5 seng-oah8. A-eng in e5 tiam3 ma7 ke chap8-chhe-a2, iu5-ki5 ti7 A-beng5 koe3-sin liau2-au7, mi7-tiam3, kam2-a2-tiam3 chin che7 khang-khoe3, long2 e7 tau3 thaN2--khi2-lai5 cho3, ju2 toa7-han3 ju2 bat ju2 kut-lat8, khang-khoe3 ju2 cho3 ju2 che7 ju2 khin5-khoai3, ma7 ju2 tit-tioh8 tak8-e5 e5 thiaN3-sim. Kheng3-tong5 i2 chit8-e5 goa7-ui7-a2-lang5, chng--li2 koan-i5 thou5-chui2, bak8-kang, chui2-tian7 teng2 chap8-chap8 tih-tih khang-khoe3, oan-na2 khioh-khioh-a2 cho3, ke-kiam2 than3. Sui-jian5 m7-si7 siaN2-mih toa7-sai, khin5-khoai3, su3-si7, lang5 to7 o-lo2, chin kin2 kap chng--li2 e5 lang5 kap cho3 chit8-khiu5.
  Chhim2-thau5 thiaN Lim5 chu2-jim7 kong2 Kheng3-tong5 in tau e5 tai7-chi3, A-eng tui3 Kheng3-tong5 e5 in3-siong7 peng7 bo5 ho2. Chu7 kio3 Chhai2-giok8 in lai5 kou3-tiam3 liau2-au7, tak8-e5 khah u7 chiap-chhiok, tui3 Kheng3-tong5 soah khou2-lian5--khi2-lai5. U7-iaN2 ke-kak-a2 oh chhoa7 kiaN2, iu5-ki5 chu7 nng7-hoe3 kap si3-hoe3 gin2-a2 chhoa7 toa7, u7 khah thiam2-thau5. ¡§A-hiong sim-koaN sit8-chai7 u7-kau3 nge7, to hiah che7 ni5--a, iau2 m7 tng2--lai5.¡¨ ¡§Kin2 choa7-ban7 e7 tng2--lai5-lah.¡¨ Siu3-tin jin7-ui5: ¡§Chng-kha-lang5 ke3 Tai5-pak, be5-tioh8 chhia-hoa5, boe7-hiau2 siuN7 m7-chiah e7 li7 ang pang3 kiaN2, siuN7 thiat liau2-au7 to7 e7 siuN7 kiaN2 siuN7 chhu3--lah.¡¨ Jit8-seng ma7 kam2-kak in bou2 u7 khah koe3-hun7: ¡§KhoaN3 Kheng3-tong5 hiah sioh gin2-a2, eng-kai boe7 phah bou2 chiah tioh8.... Ah bo5, to7-si7 siau3-lian5 khah chhong2-pong7--lah.¡¨ Sui-jian5 chit8-ke-lang5 chit8-ke-tai7, kap Kheng3-tong5 tauh8-tauh8-a2 sek8 liau2-au7, A-eng hoat-kak loe7-cheng5 na2-chhiuN7 bo5 hiah tan-sun5.
  ¡§Na7 mai3 khi3 koaiN to7 bo5 chia--e5 tai7-chi3--lah.¡¨ Kheng3-tong5 put-si5 chu7-oan3 chu7-than3. U7-iaN2 chit8-e5 chiah8-thau5-lou7-lang5, e7 hou7 thau5-ke gou7-hoe7 kam3-siu2 chu7-to7, choan5 si7 Kheng3-tong5 siau3-lian5 hong3-tong7 e5 koan-he7. ¡§Kok-hau7 pit-giap8 bo5 joa7 ku2, toe3 kang7-chng--li2 A-goan5-chek lai5 Tai5-pak cho3 sio2-kang, chiah chap8-lak8-hoe3 nia5. Hit-chun7 e5 Bin5-koan5-tang-lou7, Siong5-kang-lou7 oh, ma7 chiah khui ho2 bo5 joa7 ku2.¡¨ U7-iaN2 gou7, lak8-chap8 ni5-tai7 e5 Tai5-pak, oah8-lek8 chhiong-phoe3, si3-ke3 lau5-a2-chhu3 it-tit8 thah8--khi2-lai5, Kheng3-tong5 kho3 sin-the2 ho2, lat8-thau5 iong2, choan bau7 kang-te7 taN chng-a2, tiau3 chng-a2 e5 khang-khoe3. Sui-jian5 chhou-tang7, chiN5 kau7 lang5 to7 u7 bah, tu5 kia3 chit8-koa2 tng2--khi3, chhun--e5 tak8-e5 chio-chio--leh to7 khi3 te5-tiam3-a2 phaN7. Chit8-kun5 kau2-hiaN kau2-ti7 to7 an2-ne kiat kui-tong2, cho3-kang, chhit-tho5, sio-phah long2 kat cho3-hoe2.
  Thau5-a2 cho3-kang iau2-si7 pun2-giap8, chu7 bat Tang-mng5-kau5 liau2-au7, chng-a2 taN m7-chiaN5 taN, kui-boe2 toe3 i chhit-tho5, chiah8-chheng7, phah thian-ha7. Tang-mng5-kau5 chu7 kap lang5 piaN3 te7-poaN5, khang-chhiu2 jip8 to-tin7, pin5 taN2-khi3 phah chhut mia5-siaN, se3-bin7 chiok chheng3--e5. Kheng3-tong5 e7 hou7 lang5 kio3 ou-to7, to7-si7 toe3 i siu te7-poaN5 po2-hou7-hui3 e5 si5 hou7 lang5 ho7--e5. Ka-chai3 ou-to7 kiaN5 bo5 ku2, to7 khi3 cho3-peng--a.
  U7 lang5 kong2 cho3-peng, ho2-kiaN2 pian3 phaiN2-kiaN2, phaiN2-kiaN2 e7 pian3 ho2. Piau2-si7 kun-tiong ho2-bai2-lang5 e7 tou3 lai5 tou3 khi3. Kheng3-tong5 cho3-peng au7, sui-jian5 lou5-moa5-khui3 tai3 tiau5--leh, lou5-moa5-lang5 e5 gi7-khi3 ka chng-kha-lang5 e5 tiau5-tit8, kap lang5 boe7-bai2 cho3 tui. Chhut tiong-sim liau2-au7, ho2-un7 pun-hoat ti7 kun-hoat-chhu3 cho3 thoan5-leng7-peng, chit8-jit8 kau3 am3 u7 ki-hoe7 khoaN3-tioh8 heng5-heng5 sek-sek e5 hoan7-lang5-peng. Chia--e5 hoan7-lang5-peng lai7-te2, siong7 che7 si7 to5-peng. To5-peng pun kui2-lo7 khoan2, u7 chhu3--li2 e5 koan-he7, chhiuN7 khan-chhiu2 kap si7-toa7-lang5 boe7-hah8--lah, khan-chhiu2 chau2--khi3-lah ..... Ko3-jin5 in-sou3 u7 kiaN kan-khou2, kiaN chhut-chhau--e5, u7 kap teng2-si boe7-hah8, iau2 u7 siuN7 beh ha--chit8-chhui3, tong3 boe7 tiau5 lai5 chau2--e5. Cho3-peng cheng5 suh-tok8, kui-chhiu2 choan5 chiam-khang bat8-bat8 si7--e5, Kheng3-tong5 to7 khoaN3 kui2--a7 e5. KhoaN3-tioh8 hia--e5 hoan7-lang5, cho3-lang5 chit8-sut-sut-a2 chun-giam5, ke3-tat8 to bo5, lian5 in ka-ti7 to chu7-pok chu7-khi3. Bat u7 chit8-e5 kio3 A-pun2-a2 e5 to5-peng, chau2 liau2 chau2, lui2-chek heng5-ki5 si3-ni5, hou7 lang5 ah khi3 chhiuN2-siu pang-khiah hai2-hoaN7. Kheng3-tong5 khoaN3 i put-si5 hah-hi3, kho2-leng5 bat chiah8 tok8-phin2, ka7 sin-the2 phah-phaiN2. Tak8-jit8 ti7 hai2--nih cho3-kang, ka-ti7 keng-the2 ka-ti7: ¡§KhoaN3 e7 hou7 hai2-eng2 koah-koah--khi3-bo5, si2-si2 tiau7 siong7-ho2!¡¨ Chit8-e7 khoaN3 che7 thiaN che7, chin ka-chai3 bo5 an3-te2, phaiN2-lou7 iau2-si7 m7-thang kiaN5, bo5, chit8-si3-lang5 e7 khi3 khioh-kak--khi3. Ti7 the3-ngou2 au7 to7 bo5 koh khi3 chhoe7 tang-mng5 lau2-toa7. Ka-ti7 chhoe7 khi2-chhu3 kang-te7 cho3 soaN3-kang. Kheng3-tong5 taN chng-a2 khi2-sin, khang-khoe3 hou7 lang5 chin o-lo2. SiuN7 boe7 kau3 Tai5-pak kong2 toa7, toa7; kong2 se3, se3, ti7 kang-te7 bu5-i3-tiong lai5 tng7-tioh8 in tang-mng5 lau2-toa7. Ou3, ai3 kai2 kio3 Chia7-tang2, in-ui7 i2-keng si7 eng5-cho7-chhiuN2 e5 tang2-su7-tiuN2--louh. Chia7-tang2 khoaN3 Kheng3-tong5 cho3 soaN3-kang m7-si7 ku2-tng5, kong2 beh an-teng7 to7 ai3 chai7-giah8, khoaN3 ti7 i2-cheng5 hiaN-ti7 cho3-hoe2 kam2-cheng5, tian7-oe7 kha3--leh, soaN3-kang pian3 chai7-giah8, ka7 Kheng3-tong5 in2 jip8-lai5 hian7-chhu2-si5 chit-keng kian3-siat kong-si.
  Kheng3-tong5 siong7-pan liau2-au7, chin piaN3-si3 ma7 chin siu2 pun2-hun7. Bou2-pun2 khiam7 u7, ti7 ji7-chap8-peh-hoe3 hit-ni5 hoe5-hiong, chhoa7 kang7-chng e5 A-hiong lai5 Tai5-pak, hit-chun7 A-hiong chiah chap8-peh-hoe3 nia5. Au7--lai5 kong-si put-si5 hoat-seng kang-liau7 phang3-kiN3, hiam5-gi5 u7 lai7-chhat8. Keng-koe3 an-choan5 tiau-cha, chha5 chhut i si7 Chia7-tang2 siau7-kai3, Chia7-tang2 e5 te2-ti3 ma7 phok8 chhut--lai5. Kheng3-tong5 chhit-tho5 si5 e5 goa7-ho7 ou-to7 toe3 hian3-hian3--chhut-lai5, ki5-sit8 kap Chia7-tang2 cha2 bo5 ong2-lai5. Chia7-tang2 te2-ti3 phok8-lou7 liau2-au7, u7-iaN2 Kheng3-tong5 hoat-kak in, chhit-tho5 hong-hoat long2 bo5-kang5. Chin3-cheng5 chhit-tho5 pin5 taN2-khui3, khun2-thau5, kha-chhiu2.... Chit-ma2 tu5-liau2 gan2-kong, chhiu2-oan2, ke3-bou5 i2-goa7, i2 hap8-hoat am-hou7 hui-hoat. Kang7-khoan2 ai3 chiN5, pou7-sou3 che7, ma7 ke chin iu3-siu3. Kheng3-tong5 sui-jian5 u7 chit-e5 jin7-sek, kho2-sioh siuN ban7, ma7 bo5-kau3 thiat-te2. Kau3 u7 chit8-kang, Chia7-tang2 hou7 lang5 pong3-tiau7, kong-si to bo5 jip8-khou3 e5 kang-liau7 e7 khi3 phang3-kiN3? Kheng3-tong5 soah hou5-li2 hou5-tou5 hou7 lang5 liah8 khi3 koaiN.
  Su7-au7 cheng3-sit8 lai7-sin5 thong goa7-kui2 m7-si7 i, i put-ko3 si7 chit8-e5 sio2-chut-a2, the3-si2-kui2 nia5. Tai7-chi3 ma7 m7-si7 i sou2 chai phang3-kiN3 kang-liau7 hiah tan-sun5. Khan-lian5 kong-si lai7-te2 goan5-kang, kap ou-sia7-hoe7 kak-thau5 chiong2-chiong2 kim-chiN5 li7-ek kau-kiat. Kheng3-tong5 koaiN ti7 lai7-te2, tak8-hang7 m7-chai. Kau3 pang3--chhut-lai5, kong-si na2-chhiuN7 toa7-te7-tang7--leh, koaiN--e5 koaiN, si5--e5 si5. Kheng3-tong5 ui7-tioh8 in A-hiong, kong-si na2 leh kong-si--leh, bou2 kin2 chhoa7 tng2-lai5 chhu3--li2, chhia-hoa5-seng3 tu5-tiau7 khah iau3-kin2. Goan5-lai5 te2-te2 peh-ko3-goa7-goeh8, in A-hiong, chhu3 m7-toa3, kiaN2 m7-chhoa7, kou3 khi3 li2-sia7 than3! Chhui3 kong2 cho3 lu2-tiong, siaN2-lang5 (siang2) chai piN3 siaN2-bang2? Kheng3-tong5 khi3-chhoah-chhoah khi3 li2-sia7 thau5-mng5 chang2--leh ka7 khiu2 tng2--lai5: ¡§Kio3 li2 khi3 ka7 lang5 se2-chhia, li2 phian-phian ai3 khi3 li2-sia7, phoe5 leh chiuN7 si7--bo5?¡¨ Chhui3 kong2 boe7 soah, chhut-chhiu2 to7 ka7 hou3--loh8-khi3. Ia7 bo5 siuN7 A-hiong ui7 than3-chhi7 chit8-ke, lou7-piN se2-chhia, than3 nah u7-kau3 chiah8? Siong7-chhiaN2, ti7 li2-sia7 cho3 khang-khoe3 boe7 koaN5 boe7 joah8, lou7-piN se2-chhia kui seng-khu tam5-lok-lok, siuN5-leh-leh koh leng2-ki-ki, lian5 kui-tin7 se2-chhia-phoaN7 to kong2, pin5 A-hiong hit-pan7--e5, m7-bian2 than3 chiah-ni7-a2 kan-khou2-chiN5--lah. Kui-boe2 lian5 i ka-ti7 to hiam5 ui2-khut. Khi3 ti7 li2-sia7 piaN3-sau3 si5, saN-ko5 nng7-ko5, ko5 loh8-khi3 than3--lah. Kheng3-tong5 chhut-gak8, ng3-bang7 A-hiong gin2-a2 kou3 hou7 ho2, m7-koh, A-hiong put-si5 thau chhu--chhut-khi3, ui7-tioh8 an2-ne, ang-bou2 si5-siong5 oan-ke. Kheng3-tong5 chit8-e7 khi3--khi2-lai5, m7-si7 kun5-thau5-bu2 khian--loh8-khi3, to7-si7 sau3-chhiu2-peN3 ham2--loh8-khi3, cha-pou-lang5 chhiu2-thau5 tang7, A-hiong put-si5 hou7 but8 kah ou-chheN, chit8-pai2 hiam2-hiam2-a2 kha-kut hou7 kong3-tng7, bin7-siong7 ma7 chha chit8-tiam2-a2 hou7 siau7 kah phoa3-siuN3--khi3. Boe7-kham lih oan kui2-pai2, A-hiong cho3 i soan-chau2--lah.
  ¡§U7 lang5 to7-si7 ai3 chhia-hoa5, chiah e7 tui7-loh8 ian-hoe.¡¨ Siu3-tin chit8-khau2 jin7-teng7: ¡§Chiah ji7-chap8-ji7-hoe3 nia5, hou7 lang5 lang7--leh, hoan7-chian7 toe3 lang5 kiaN5--lah.¡¨ Kheng3-tong5 jin7-ui5 kha-chhng-au7 it-teng7 u7 lang5 sai2-long7, ah bo5, in A-hiong boe7 chau2 kah bo5 khoaN3-kiN3 lang5. Chha5 cheng5 chha5 au7, chha5 chhut A-hiong oh8 e7-hiau2 poah8-kiau2, iau2 khiam3 lang5 chiN5, koh boe7 se3-tiau5--leh! Siong7-chhiaN2 poah8-tioh8 kui-me5 kui-jit8, hou7 Kheng3-tong5 chin tan-sim. Kiau2-tiuN5 Kheng3-tong5 bat kou3--tioh8, che7--tioh8 kui-kang, tak8-hang7 lang5 hong7-thai7 pian7-pian7. Lim--e5, chiah8--e5, sng2--e5, ..., tak8-hang7 to eng3-hu3--li2. Chi2-iau3 khou li2 che7 leh poah8, mai3 peh--khi2-lai5 to7 ho2. Kheng3-tong5 siong7 kiaN in A-hoing boe7-hiau2 siuN7, m7-bat khin-tang7, the5-sin5 hit-bi7--e5 na7 gong7-gong7 khi3 hou7 lang5 chhi7--chit8-chhui3-a2, he, he to7 lian5-hoe5--louh!
  Sui-jian5 chin piaN3-si3 chhoe7, chang2 bo5 chong5-kiaN3-jin5, na2 bo5-thau5 kong-an3--leh. A-hiong chu7 an2-ne bo5-siau bo5-sit. Kong-si e5 tian7-oe7 kap chhu3--li2 e5 chu7-chi2 i eng3-kai iau2 e7 ki3--tit, chi2-iau3 chit8-thong tian7-oe7 iah chit8-tiuN phoe, m7-koan2 thiN-piN hai2-kak, Kheng3-tong5 long2 e7 chhoa7 i tng2--lai5, ng3-bang7 chit8-kang, tan2-tioh8 in A-hiong hoe5-sim tng2-i3, hap8-ke thoan5-iN5--lah.
